And to learn more about the original trend that started it all, this video
provides a glimpse of Kappabashi in Tokyo, a district devoted to supplying the
restaurant industry, including with _shokuhin sanpuru_.

As well as this video, which gives an overview of how Japanese food samples
are actually made.

